sentences: Donavon Frankenreiter (born December 10, 1972 in Downey, California, United States) is an American musician and surfer.
His debut self-titled album was released in 2004 on Brushfire Records through Universal Music.

In November 2007, Donavon toured throughout Brazil on the Mostra Alma Surf Festival with bands, Animal Liberation Orchestra, G. Love and Matt Costa, along with Surf Artists Jay Alders, Nathan Gibbs, CÃ©line Chat, Surf Photographer Sean Davey, and Surf Film Maker Sunny Abberton.
